THIS. This is just so spot on.&#xD;
Dont get scarey by the name pink this such a delightful S&amp;C vape. Even for me who has trouble finding good ones due to Strawberry insensitivity &#xD;
I have never tastes Strawberry so upfront in any way before which doesnt mean that its lacking in the cream department. &#xD;
&#xD;
What i like most about this recipe is that it has tastes good in any style of vaping i could think of &#xD;
RTA (Serpent Mini): Insanely tasty blend of S&amp;C perfectly balanced &#xD;
High Wattage RDA: Highly intense sweet pounding of flavor on the tounge &#xD;
Flavor RDA (Hadaly): Here is where the recipe really shines with a complex and sweet cream toped with the delicious play of the 3 strawberry flavors which make strawberry tastable even for someone who usually cant taste any strawberries at all.&#xD;
&#xD;
Mix this up. You wont regret it
